definitions.definition: Any of various freshwater crustaceans : crayfish .
definitions.label_groups: Southern US , New York and Western US

definitions.definition: Any of various marine crustaceans, rock lobster ; especially Jasus lalandii , the Cape crawfish .
An English-Canadian . Used in some corners of Quebec (including the Gaspé ).
